 {"id":"git_safety_guard-pbte.9","title":"[Cross] Environment variable configuration (DCG_VERBOSE, etc.)","description":"# Task: Environment Variable Configuration

## Background
Support environment variables for configuration alongside CLI flags and config files.

## Variables
- DCG_VERBOSE (0-3): Verbosity level
- DCG_FORMAT (text|json|sarif): Default output format
- DCG_CONFIG: Config file path override
- DCG_NO_COLOR: Disable colored output
- DCG_QUIET: Suppress non-error output
- DCG_HOOK_TIMEOUT_MS: Hook evaluation timeout

## Precedence
CLI flags > Environment variables > Config file > Defaults

## Implementation
Use clap's env feature for seamless integration.

## Acceptance Criteria
